headline: Cadence Design Systems (CDNS): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q3 Earnings?
summary: Cadence Design Systems has followed the market’s trajectory closely, rising in tandem with the S&P 500 over the past six months. The stock has climbed by 11% to $340.92 per share while the index has gained 13.6%.
